        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Third solution: Since both sides are continuous in each positive fit sent to rose the dus by iking is al some of the a; tend to zero). Put ri = bi/ai; then the given inequality is equivalent to",
        "bbox": [
          0.5545112823553365,
