        "observed_type": "list_item",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "one such sum with k terms for each of k = 1,...,n (and clearly no others). To see this, note that if n = a1 + a2 + ...+ ak With a1 ≤ a2<.. < ak< a1 + 1, then",
        "bbox": [
          0.12781956109678008,
          0.18168604690333784,
          0.48872180210027477,
          0.22395833337067117
        ],
        "order": 5
      },
